org.metastatic.sexp4j

Class StreamingParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.metastatic.sexp4j.StreamingParser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdvancedStreamingParser, CanonicalStreamingParser

    public abstract class StreamingParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Base class for a streaming parser.

    To use a streaming parser, you register one or more StreamingParserCallback instances with this object, which will be called as expressions are read from the underlying input stream.
